---
import HumanLayout from '../layouts/HumanLayout.astro';
---

<HumanLayout title="简历 | 姜华" description="产品及用户运营专家 · 15年互联网实战经验">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    
    {/* Header */}
    <header class="mb-16">
      <h1 class="font-human text-4xl md:text-5xl text-human-text mb-4">姜华</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-mid">产品及用户运营专家 · 15年+实战经历</p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-gray-light">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
          18913138955（微信同）
        </span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          Faraway1314@163.com
        </span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
          Base地不设限（现驻杭州）
        </span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"/></svg>
          硕士（悉尼科技大学）
        </span>
      </div>
    </header>

    {/* 求职意向 */}
    <section class="mb-16 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-human-bg">
      <h2 class="font-human text-xl text-human-text mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-aurora-green/10 text-aurora-green flex items-center justify-center text-sm">01</span>
        求职意向
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-human-text">
        <p><span class="text-gray-light">目标行业：</span>酒旅 / 本地生活 / 养老健康 / 产业互联网 / AI应用落地</p>
        <p><span class="text-gray-light">目标职位：</span>AI应用运营 / 用户增长专家 / 商业化运营 / ToB业务增长 / 产业互联网运营</p>
        <p><span class="text-gray-light">发展预期：</span>聚焦通过AI工具助力垂类行业建设自动化工作流程；通过搭建行业智能体带动业务的精细化运营与商业化增长</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* 核心能力总结 */}
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-human text-2xl text-human-text mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-aurora-blue/10 text-aurora-blue flex items-center justify-center text-sm">02</span>
        核心能力总结
      </h2>
      <p class="text-human-text mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        作为一名拥有15年+实战经验的互联网运营专家，我经历了从同程艺龙的创业上市期到美团、蚂蚁集团等一线大厂的成熟期，积累了丰富的ToC产品运营与商业化操盘经验。核心竞争力构建在四大支柱之上：
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-human-bg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">🎯</span>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-human-text">产品运营能力</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-mid leading-relaxed">
            懂产品的运营操盘手。主导"动态打包"技术流程改造实现规模化扩张；在支付宝出行频道主导架构改版，显著提升流量分发效率。
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-human-bg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">📈</span>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-human-text">用户增长能力</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-mid leading-relaxed">
            深谙全生命周期管理，具备千万级用户增长模型实战经验。主导美团酒店会员体系从0到1重构；统筹线下获客专项，累计获取数千万新用户。
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-human-bg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">💰</span>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-human-text">商业化变现能力</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-mid leading-relaxed">
            管理亿级流量的商业化变现。建立外部KA分销渠道接入规则；在存量博弈阶段通过精细化运营挖掘用户消费场景跃迁机会点。
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-human-bg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">🤖</span>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-human-text">AI产品落地经验</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-mid leading-relaxed">
            主导支付宝"出行AI助手"专项，负责Prompt优化与场景定义，打通从用户咨询到服务购买的商业闭环。积极探索"AI+运营"复合能力。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* 工作经历 */}
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-human text-2xl text-human-text mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-resonance-gold/10 text-resonance-gold flex items-center justify-center text-sm">03</span>
        工作经历
      </h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-10">
        {/* 蚂蚁 */}
        <div class="relative pl-6 border-l-2 border-aurora-green/30">
          <div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-aurora-green/20 border-2 border-aurora-green"></div>
          <div class="mb-2">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-human-text">蚂蚁集团 · 支付宝数字出行酒旅事业部</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-light">平台运营专家 | 2024.07 — 至今 | 汇报：平台运营负责人 | 团队：10人</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-human-text text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            全面负责支付宝出行频道的用户增长策略、流量分发机制及商业化运营。在成熟的支付工具属性下，探索内容化、服务化运营，提升用户访问频次与交易转化；同时作为核心负责人推进AI在运营团队内的组织能力升级。
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-mid">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-aurora-green shrink-0">▸</span>
              <span><strong>AI组织能力升级：</strong>主导团队AI助手（内部openclaw）技能培训项目，2026年4月落地培训，推动团队AI化能力升级</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-aurora-green shrink-0">▸</span>
              <span><strong>出行AI助手：</strong>主导产品设计，构建万级Query库，通过RLHF持续优化，问题解决率从30%提升至60%+；在AI回复中植入SKU推荐，探索商业闭环</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-aurora-green shrink-0">▸</span>
              <span><strong>频道改版：</strong>基于数据分析优化首屏金刚位与信息流分配逻辑，针对不同画像展示差异化服务，从人工分配升级为算法驱动</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        {/* 美团 */}
        <div class="relative pl-6 border-l-2 border-aurora-blue/30">
          <div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-aurora-blue/20 border-2 border-aurora-blue"></div>
          <div class="mb-2">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-human-text">美团 · 酒店事业部</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-light">产品运营部C端用户运营负责人 / 分销业务负责人 | 2019.09 — 2024.06 | 汇报：产品运营部负责人 | 团队：7人</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-human-text text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            在美团酒店业务成熟期，负责挖掘新增长曲线。核心覆盖用户增长、会员体系运营及分销渠道优化，通过精细化运营提升间夜量、GMV与用户LTV。
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-mid">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-aurora-blue shrink-0">▸</span>
              <span><strong>会员体系重构：</strong>主导搭建普银金白钻等级权益，引入房型升级、延迟退房等高感知权益；建立RFM用户分层模型，中高等级会员贡献间夜量持续提升</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-aurora-blue shrink-0">▸</span>
              <span><strong>线下获客专项：</strong>在酒店前台、景区入口等场景铺设物料，优化"线下扫码预订-店内服务"链路，累计获取数千万线下新用户</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-aurora-blue shrink-0">▸</span>
              <span><strong>分销商业化：</strong>对接差旅平台、图商等外部B端渠道，协调产研完成API对接，优化商旅分销供给结构</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        {/* 同程艺龙 */}
        <div class="relative pl-6 border-l-2 border-resonance-gold/30">
          <div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-resonance-gold/20 border-2 border-resonance-gold"></div>
          <div class="mb-2">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-human-text">同程艺龙 · 平台产品中心</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-light">产品总监 | 2017.08 — 2019.09 | 汇报：集团CMO | 团队：30人</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-human-text text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            统筹同程艺龙两大品牌自营app平台的产品规划与运营，创新孵化国际化业务（travelgo站点，hopego前身）。
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-mid">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-resonance-gold shrink-0">▸</span>
              <span><strong>国际化从0到1：</strong>组建国际化团队，完成繁体中文、英语站点及微信小程序搭建，配套多语言客服与支付结算体系</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-resonance-gold shrink-0">▸</span>
              <span><strong>流量矩阵：</strong>孵化百度小程序、安卓快应用等新兴入口，实现平台DAU稳步提升，降低单一渠道依赖</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        {/* 同程旅游 */}
        <div class="relative pl-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200">
          <div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-gray-100 border-2 border-gray-300"></div>
          <div class="mb-2">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-human-text">同程旅游 · 周边自由行项目</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-light">运营总监 → 项目总经理 | 2013.04 — 2017.07 | 核心标签：内部创业、从0到1、爆款操盘</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-human-text text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            作为核心创始成员参与周边游事业部组建，见证团队从3人扩张至千人规模。负责商业模式设计、供应链整合及市场营销策略。
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-mid">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-gray-light shrink-0">▸</span>
              <span><strong>"十元度周末"：</strong>单场销售酒店间夜量突破20,000+，获客超70,000+，以极低营销成本引爆长三角市场</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-gray-light shrink-0">▸</span>
              <span><strong>"动态打包"系统：</strong>实现用户前端自由组合、后端库存实时调用的自动化流程，支持业务从百万级向亿级营收跨越</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* 核心项目 */}
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-human text-2xl text-human-text mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-aurora-green/10 text-aurora-green flex items-center justify-center text-sm">04</span>
        核心项目经历
      </h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-human-bg">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-2 mb-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-human-text text-lg">美团酒店会员体系重构与全生命周期运营</h3>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-light bg-gray-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">2019 — 2023</span>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <p><span class="text-gray-light font-medium">背景：</span>美团酒店面临行业存量博弈，原有会员体系权益单一，高价值用户流失风险增加，LTV挖掘不足。</p>
            <p><span class="text-gray-light font-medium">行动：</span>基于RFM模型对亿级用户精准分层，定义5级成长路径；确定以"会员折扣""房型升级"为核心的高感知权益，联合美团外卖推出跨场景权益。</p>
            <p><span class="text-aurora-green font-medium">结果：</span>中高等级会员贡献间夜量占比持续提升；参与会员价格权益输出的酒店数量持续提升。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-human-bg">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-2 mb-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-human-text text-lg">支付宝"出行AI助手"创新专项</h3>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-light bg-gray-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">2024 — 至今</span>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <p><span class="text-gray-light font-medium">背景：</span>大模型技术爆发，但ToC商业化落地场景稀缺。支付宝出行频道面临服务入口深、咨询效率低、变现手段单一的问题。</p>
            <p><span class="text-gray-light font-medium">行动：</span>主导定义智能行程规划、旅游线路规划、公交地铁站点查询三大场景；批量生产预设query教育市场；从人工生产query升级为AI自动化生产。</p>
            <p><span class="text-aurora-blue font-medium">结果：</span>query生产效率提升100倍以上；从追求DAU转向追求高质量query的服务挂载率和用户使用频次。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-human-bg">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-2 mb-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-human-text text-lg">同程周边游"十元度周末"引爆战役</h3>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-light bg-gray-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">2013</span>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <p><span class="text-gray-light font-medium">背景：</span>同程进军周边游蓝海，品牌认知度低，用户习惯尚未养成，急需低成本高爆发获客手段。</p>
            <p><span class="text-gray-light font-medium">行动：</span>筛选高品质五星酒店与热门景区，通过补贴打造"10元"极致价格锚点；设计"限量抢购"机制，全域媒体地毯式传播。</p>
            <p><span class="text-resonance-gold font-medium">结果：</span>单场获客7万+，销售间夜超2万；开创OTA行业"爆款引流、长尾盈利"经典打法。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* 教育背景 */}
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-human text-2xl text-human-text mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-aurora-blue/10 text-aurora-blue flex items-center justify-center text-sm">05</span>
        教育背景
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-human-bg">
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-human-text">悉尼科技大学 (UTS)</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-mid">旅游管理 · 硕士</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-light mt-1 md:mt-0">2009.02 — 2010.12</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-human-bg">
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-human-text">苏州大学</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-mid">旅游管理 · 本科</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-light mt-1 md:mt-0">2003.09 — 2007.06</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* 专业技能 */}
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-human text-2xl text-human-text mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-resonance-gold/10 text-resonance-gold flex items-center justify-center text-sm">06</span>
        专业技能与语言
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-human-bg">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-human-text mb-4">专业技能</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['用户全生命周期管理', 'AARRR模型', '会员体系搭建', '分销渠道管理', '产品规划', 'UI/UX优化', '数据分析', '漏斗分析', '归因分析', 'OKR拆解', 'KPI绩效', '团队文化建设'].map(tag => (
              <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-mid text-xs">{tag}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-human-bg">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-human-text mb-4">语言 & 软技能</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-mid">
